00:21:25.740 --> 00:21:26.940
they'd cancelled.

00:21:26.940 --> 00:21:34.200
So I need another term
and it turns out to be --

00:21:34.200 --> 00:21:35.680
I'll just write it down.

00:21:35.680 --> 00:21:41.360
It's got to depend on x
minus c*t and x plus c*t

00:21:41.360 --> 00:21:50.500
and it's this -- it's the
integral of this velocity dx.

00:21:50.500 --> 00:21:55.840
I won't -- there's no reason
to take time to derive that.

00:21:55.840 --> 00:21:59.190
I think it's right
and could check.

00:21:59.190 --> 00:22:00.290
Right.

00:22:00.290 --> 00:22:09.510
So what this means is that
the initial velocity is --

00:22:09.510 --> 00:22:12.560
it's entering,
somehow, all along --

00:22:12.560 --> 00:22:23.600
somehow the initial velocity
is affecting things within this

00:22:23.600 --> 00:22:31.520
cone, this characteristic
cone that's defined

00:22:31.520 --> 00:22:34.480
by the characteristic lines.

00:22:34.480 --> 00:22:37.880
In two dimensions, that cone
will really look like a cone.

00:22:37.880 --> 00:22:40.300
It'll look like an
ice cream cone --

00:22:40.300 --> 00:22:41.950
